{"tid":1643683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗你老母蒙面法！！原來一齊集體蒙面唱歌可能唔犯法？？","createTime":"2019-10-10T08:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T02:21:02.000Z","uid":30138,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18330b8e40ea2c1d402b2b47da5625dda6469de2","tid":1643683,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾《禁蒙面法》實施左3日，已經有77個人足因為咁而被拘捕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有手足係街帶口罩都亂俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左我地日日都帶黑口罩出街！我地要諗多D抗爭方法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返蒙面法，話係參與集結既時候蒙面就會收皮。<br />\n但呢，所謂集結，睇返《公安條例》第245章既其中一個講法係&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n集會並不包括任何純粹為社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教或慈善目的；葬禮目的；任何公共機構的目的（例如由政府舉辦的公眾論壇）；或根據任何條例履行任何職務而舉行的任何聚集或集結。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我係條街好多人一齊busking算唔算康樂活動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我係街同一堆人一齊做蒙面歌手咁得唔得呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿！咁如果遇到狗咬，叫你玩busking時除口罩，問你係度做咩，咪如實答佢玩緊busking<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要記注，依家蒙面法有講popo可以係公眾地方要求任何人士取下口罩或面罩，咁玩busking佢叫除到時咪除囉，佢問係做咩玩busking要帶口罩，咁我放lunch夾band驚俾老闆認到，咪帶，唔犯法卦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾《禁蒙面法》：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/antimask/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sb.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fantimask%2Findex.htm&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=313e68bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/antimask/index.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n當抗爭成為日常，Lunch Break都可以有唔同抗爭。一齊連結更多區內打工巴絲，喚醒更多人，互相撐落去！  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理唱又得，諗下lunch有咩可以玩做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返工好悶嫁嘛！lunch break 諗下有咩活動搞，差差電～繼續做返工奴～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUN1eV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUN1eV.jpg&h=2dec4b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地有個tg gp，各區打工仔可以入黎傾下平時lunch break 有咩做～<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/flashlunch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fflashlunch&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=86a30950\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/flashlunch</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日旺角好似有人叫一齊快閃：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mkbrosiscome\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmkbrosiscome&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=80a0cda2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mkbrosiscome</a> <br />\n<br />\n召集更多區手足加入！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ada1d04ea12436f222a8483de22a4b788964b1","tid":1643683,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"召集更多區手足加入！！！"},{"pid":"ca8f63f63cadb1774e5539fc709d590ec8396887","tid":1643683,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:58:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9fbd5c55d5f66f1e82b21bd1b7483ce84e2a2850","tid":1643683,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f1e19daefeaef15df41cb824dfa1498ce67c2e75","tid":1643683,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8f4b4258d15f616a1424f84aa4f38f3b